      Hirsch, Laurence, "Home-Builder Stocks Punished Too Much?"
      interview in 
      
        National Mortgage News
      
      , December 17, 2001, p. 16.
    

      "Home Building Plus," 
      
        Forbes
      
      , March 8, 1999, p. 89.
    

